    <string name="permissions">Permissions</string>
    <string name="permission_desc">Dear Customer,\nIn order to process and disburse your loan quickly, we need to collect certain permissions, including access to your LOCATION, CAMERA, PHONE STATE, NOTIFICATIONS, INSTALLED APPLICATIONS, SMS MESSAGES, and CALL LOGS.\nPlease grant the necessary permissions as specified below.</string>
    <string name="permission_call_title">COLLECTION OF CALL RECORDS</string>
    <string name="permission_call_content">In order to ensure that real users use the app in a normal environment, rather than using a simulator for fraudulent behavior, we need to obtain your call records, including phone number, name, and call time. The call records information will be uploaded to %s and will not be shared with third parties.</string>
    <string name="permission_sms_title">SMS</string>
    <string name="permission_sms_content">We collect all your SMS data but only monitor your messages related to financial transactions. To be specific, we will monitor the name of the sender, the description and the amount of transaction to perform credit risk assessment. This enables faster and quicker loan disbursal. No personal SMS data is monitored, read, stored or shared.</string>
    <string name="permissions_notification_title">NOTIFICATION</string>
    <string name="permissions_notification_content">Turn on message notifications to receive loan order progress notifications and service messages as soon as possible to avoid missing important information and help improve your user experience.Please read carefully and agree to the following agreement in order to use the APP.</string>
    <string name="permission_location_title">LOCATION</string>
    <string name="permission_location_content">User location helps to locate and verify the address which helps in making better credit risk decisions and fasten the Know Your Customer(KYC) process.</string>
    <string name="permission_camera_title">CAMERA</string>
    <string name="permission_camera_content">Camera access is required so that user can easily scan or capture identity documents etc. and save time by allowing us to auto-fill the required data and helps in improving the user journey and experience.</string>
    <string name="permission_phone_title">PHONE STATE</string>
    <string name="permission_phone_content">Like your phone’s unique device identifier, as this information helps us in uniquely identifying a user, so that we can detect and prevent any unauthorized device from acting on your behalf. This enables us to detect fraud and manage risks better.</string>
    <string name="permission_installed_title">INSTALLED APPLICATIONS</string>
    <string name="permission_installed_content">We will get a list of installed applications data information, including application name, package name, installation time update time, version name and version code of each installed application on the device to evaluate your credit value and enrich your personal data with pre approved custom loan offers.</string>
    <string name="permission_calendar_title">COLLECTION OF CALENDAR</string>
    <string name="permission_calendar_content">In order to improve your experience, we would like to access your calendar. This will help us automatically add repayment reminders and important loan dates for you, ensuring that you don’t miss any important information. We take your privacy very seriously and promise to use this data only with your consent and not for other purposes.</string>
